      },
      "date": "2023-10-23 08:36:49.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Abandoned\n > \n > replaced by https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/52798\n\nWhile I think the 52798 patch is useful in any case, it is also important to reserve the fields for the filter_fid and lustre_ost_attrs in the master branch so that there are not other changes that might be incompatible.  It doesn't need all of the changes in this patch, but at least the struct definitions.",
