        "subject": "EX-8038 csdc: reserve compression info in LMA EA/filter_fid",
        "message": "EX-8038 csdc: reserve compression info in LMA EA/filter_fid\n\nStore compression information as part of layout information in\nOST-object's LMA EA, filter_fid, and PFID, lfsck could use it to\nrecover the MDT-object layout EA from orphan OST-object(s).\n\nFor the purpose of compatibility with the existing OST-objects and\nwire data protocol, this patch append the compression information in\ncorresponding structures, and rename the existing layout member\nto layout_base, and name the compression info member as layout_compr.\nThe structures have been changed is as such:\n\nlu_orphan_rec_v3        orphan OST-object\nobdo                    general attribute in wire data to server\nfilter_fid              self/parent FID stored on server objects\n\nSigned-off-by: Bobi Jam <bobijam@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I68f50d9d3ec971e00aaabbc6bad2ab73da3b9a65\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
